                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The party is at a crossroads and must defeat the Democrats to survive.
                    Augustans need to rally and get out the vote. No vote can safely be cast for a
                    Democrat.</summary>
